            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1661183913109-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cooked rice </strong>to the <strong>Mexican-style tomato sauce </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Top with the <strong>torn mozzarella</strong> and cook, covered, for 2 min or until the mozzarella has started to melt – this is your <strong>cheesy Mexican-style rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1661183916246-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1661183916246-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
